org.ametiste.metrics.mock

Class MockMetricsVerifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ametiste.metrics.mock.MockMetricsVerifier

  • public class MockMetricsVerifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Verify chain with methods to verify specific conditions of metric registration - type of metric (count, time), number of times registered and values of registered metrics. Created on 24.07.2014.
    Since:
    0.1.0
